sequenceDiagram
  actor Parent
  participant App as CareBridge app
  participant Caregiver
  participant Contact as Priority 1 contact
  Parent->>App: Tap I need help
  App->>App: Escalate reminder and create alert
  App-->>Caregiver: Show active emergency alert
  App-->>Contact: Notify (demo-local)
  Contact->>App: I am going to help
  App-->>Caregiver: Show accepted contact and timeline
  Caregiver->>App: Resolve emergency
  App->>App: Record resolution and close alert
